Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对圣母玛莉亚 保~密~哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在释迦牟尼的庭院里的众生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也带着菩萨般古朴的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在悟道的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是浅灰色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.51,0:00:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让裙子上的褶痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.15,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.15,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是没有裙子的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦~~ 裙子不可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想穿啊~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较希望是丁字裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.41,0:00:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该不是听你们的意见的时候吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 从头再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞什么飞机啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好不容易聚在一起 机会难得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.74,0:00:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练一练说不定以后会派上用场…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.69,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的 不行不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人要是撞上这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.79,0:00:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好可是会惊吓过度昏过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说成是「这种东西」也有点过分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.18,0:00:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 我们绞尽脑汁才想出来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.03,0:00:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦! 快回去! 不要废话!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.05,0:01:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.00,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身体不由自主地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做朋友的话 从现在开始也可以哦~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.55,0:01:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不太可能了吧…


